nodes.text: Mororororosc Valley was a valley on Ipisestec. Athlete Manac-Nebut hailed from Mororororosc.

Mororororosc Valley was mentioned in Monsters and Aliens from George Lucas, a book published in 1993. Lucasfilm employee Leland Chee, who maintains the Holocron continuity database, has indicated that information contained in the book is non-canonical.
